# Pokémon Moon 
### Any% Primarina notes

----

**Source**: [Original Notes by Wartab](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wpGbRZFX61OGna0bFDfDA-g7mqQDAhwORln2FtkSIMA/edit?tab=t.0)

:::card{theme=warning}

### Before the Run starts:

*You can prepare a save file at your bed before starting the run. DO NOT set any setting before hand as they are part of the run*   ![Start File](start.png)

----

- Select the **Boy** character   

:info[*Girl loses around 3 seconds to recieving the Make-Up Bag from Lillie in Hau'Oli*]{color=grey}
- Pick a 1 character name *'A' for example*

----

**Time is a important factor of this run, you have 2 Options:**
- **9:00** means night time. This skips a small bit of text in the Altar of the Moone cutscene
- **18:00** means day time. This will make your earlygame easier as Yungoos is the encounter instead of Rattata, which is much easier to run from *(recommended for beginners)*   

*Either of these times means you will **prevent Hail** on Victory Road which occurs between 06:00 and 11:59*   

----

**Make sure to include a soft reset of the game or boot from 3DS Home Screen in your submitted footage if you would like your run to be leaderboard valid**

:::

----


## The Notes

:::card{theme=info}
**Options:**
- Text Speed - **Fast**
- Battle Effects - **Off**
- Battle Style - **Set**
- *(Button Mode    **L=A**)*   

*Setting the Button Mode to L=A is more comfortable for a lot of runners,  but you lose about 5 seconds to doing this when being introduced to the Poké Finder in Hau’Oli City.*
:::

:::dropdown{title="More Detailed Directions" theme="error"}
- Head oustide your room and talk to Kukui
- Go grab your bag
- Follow Kukui to Iki Town
- Follow Lillie through Mahalo Trail
- Save Nebby on bridge
:::

Pick :info[**Popplio**]{color=blue}   

*Optionally, you can check your Popplio’s stats directly after obtaining it. This takes about 10 seconds, but lets you detect if your Popplio is good enough much earlier.*   


:::card{theme=info}
**Pokémon Refresh:**
- Feed 3 Beans.
- Pet 6 times:   

*Nose -> Right Eye -> Nose -> Left Eye -> Nose -> Right Eye.*
:::

- Try to leave Iki Town

:::if{source="Popplio" condition="speed=(19- / x / x)" theme=info}
Your Popplio's speed is too low. It is a RESET
:::

:::if{source="Popplio" condition="spa=(# / 7- / x)" theme=info}
Your Popplio's special attack is too low. It is a RESET
:::

:::::trainer[ Hau 1]
  :::pokemon[Litten]
    - Water Gun x2
  :::
:::::

If didn't already, check Popplio's level 5 stats at the level up screen and then level 6 stats. 

:::if{source="Popplio" condition="defense=(8- / x / x)" theme=info level=6}
Your Popplio's defense is low. This may cause the run to be more difficult; consider resetting.
:::

:info[**FREE HEAL**]{color=pink}

Head to Route 1 to the right of your house.

* **Route 1:** Catch the forced **Pikipek**.

:::::trainer[Youngster Jimmy]
  :::pokemon[Rattata]{info="Outspeed at 10+ Speed (x / 4+ / 4+)" infoColor=blue}
    - Water Gun x2
  :::
:::::

**→ Check if you have 10 or 11 Sp. Def, this is bad Sp. Def.**

:info[**FREE HEAL**]{color=pink}

:::::trainer[Hau 2]
  :::pokemon[Pichu]
    - Water Gun x3
  :::
  :::pokemon[Litten]
    - Water Gun x2
    ::damage[Litten's Scratch]{source="Popplio" offensive=false movePower=40 level=7 evs=0 opponentLevel=7 opponentStat=15 combatStages=0--5}
  :::
:::::

:info[**FREE HEAL**]{color=pink}

* **Refresh:** Pet (2 beans, 3 pets) before entering Pokémon Center.

:::if{source="Popplio" condition="spdef=10-11" level=7}
### Early Shopping :info[10-11 Sp.Def (0 - 16 / x / x) at Lvl 7]{Color=blue}
> #### Buy (Left Vendor)
> - 20 Repels (^^)
> - 1 Awakening (<^)
> - 2 Antidotes (^^)
:::

- **PC:** Deposit Pikipek.
- **Cafe:** Talk to the guy for a **Rare Candy**.

