## Route 2
- Head North to Route 2
- Perform Krystal skip by briefly running into the grass and hugging the corner (this will take some practice to hit consistently!)
![KrystalSkip](krystalskip.gif)

:::if{source="Popplio" condition="speed=(0 - 26 / 0 - 11 / 0 - 3)"}
- If you are dead to Peck, do the following
- **Before Kaleb:** Open Bag -> Potion, Repel (Do not reapply) and disable Exp.Share.
:::   


:::::::trainer[Preschooler Kaleb]
  :::::pokemon[Spearow]
    - :info[faster at 17+ Speed (27+ / 12+ / 4+)]{color=blue}
